ch.ethz.rtc.kernel
Class SegmentListIterator

java.lang.Object
  ch.ethz.rtc.kernel.SegmentListIterator

public class SegmentListIterator
extends java.lang.Object

SegmentListIterator provides an iterator that iterates over the single curve segments of a segment list.
